request.description:
Example request:

    POST /oauth/token
    {
        "client_id": "example-client-id",
        "client_secret": "example-client-secret"
    }

Example success response:

    {
        "access_token": "",
        "token_type": "Bearer",
        "expires_in": 1800
    }

Example error response:

    {
        "error": "invalid_client",
        "error_description": "Client authentication failed"
    }
